snippet.title: Super Mario 64: Decades Later - Release Trailer V1.0.3
snippet.description:
This project aims to recreate and reimagine vanilla SM64 levels from memory and remove stars or sections that felt too repetitive or just weren't fun in my eyes.

That said, some levels will be similar to vanilla while others will feel like fully new levels, because of how bad the originals were e.g. Course 15.

If you desire new stuff, the endgame close to 150 stars is filled with new original stages kinda like SM64DS had new levels.

Good luck and have fun!

The Download comes with a few extra things besides the patch, so make sure to check them out. On RHC the extras aren't provided, so make sure to get this here as well.
DL V1.0.3: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XKUKy6bxhoJtfvNhI-TnQzhRfrVkcRKH/view
